title: Le Boutique Du Skate : Laurent-Nicolas Paquin
description: Laurent has recently gained part ownership in a Quebec City skateshop, Le Boutique Du Skate as well as start his own skateboard brand Crapsack. I was in Quebec over the fall and learned a little more about what he has going on.
